  "Description": {
    "English": "A replica of the mysterious orb utilized by Polo's Quicksilver Synthesis Companion.<br><br>The physical properties of the orb are forever shifting in strangely rhythmic patterns: temperature, radioactivity and density all fluctuating to an unheard song.",
